data.description: Enjoy the beautiful Mountian setting of this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom Scottsdale home located on a quiet cul-de-sac in the wonderful community of Saddleview.  The home features 12' ceilings, skylights, a bonus media/game room, fireplace, and an attached 2-car garage. The primary ensuite bedroom provides direct access to the attractive walled backyard and gorgeous pool. The Mayo Clinic, golfing, shopping, dining and much more are all just a short drive away.  This home offers a compelling opportunity to the fortunate new owner.
